<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="262" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="7.[132,776,822,1071]" pageId="7" pageNumber="262">
<bibRefCitation author="Correll" box="[132,289,853,880]" firstAuthor="Correll" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" pagination="1 - 20" refId="ref6537" refString="CORRELL O. S. 1941. - Studies in Isochilus, Mormodes and Hexalectris. Botanical Museum Leaflets, Harvard University 10: 1 - 20. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / p. 295158" type="journal article" year="1941">Correll (1941)</bibRefCitation>
, followed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Schultes" box="[429,601,853,880]" firstAuthor="Schultes" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" refId="ref7688" refString="SCHULTES R. E. 1960. - Native Orchids of Trinidad and Tobago. International Series of Monographs on Pure and Applied Biology: Botany Division. Vol. 3. Pergamon Press Inc., Los Angeles, California, 275 p." type="book" year="1960">Schultes (1960)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Hamer" box="[612,769,853,880]" firstAuthor="Hamer" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" refId="ref7083" refString="HAMER F. 1974. - Las orquideas de El Salvador: The orchids of El Salvador, Die Orchiden El Salvadors. Vol. 2. Direccion de Publicaciones, Ministerio de Educacion, San Salvador, 426 p." type="book" year="1974">Hamer (1974)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Bellone &amp; Chiron" box="[132,398,885,911]" firstAuthor="Bellone" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" pagination="1 - 63" refId="ref6262" refString="BELLONE R. &amp; CHIRON G. 2003. - Inventaire provisoire commente des especes d'orchidees de Guyane. Richardiana 3: 1 - 63." type="journal article" year="2003">Bellone &amp; Chiron (2003)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Vasquez" box="[408,622,885,911]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Vasquez" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" refId="ref8284" refString="VASQUEZ R., IBISCH P. L., LEY A. &amp; NOWICKI C. 2004. - Los generos y especies de las Laeliinae, in VASQUEZ R. &amp; IBISCH P. L. (eds), Orquideas de Bolivia. Diversidad y estado de conservacion. Vol. 2. Laeliinae, Polystachinae, Sobraliinae con actualizacion y complementacion de Pleurothallidinae. Fundacion Amigos de la Naturaleza, Santa Cruz de la Sierra, Bolivia: 265." type="journal volume" year="2004">
Vásquez 
<emphasis box="[497,546,885,911]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="262">et al.</emphasis>
(2004)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Chiron &amp; Bellone" firstAuthor="Chiron" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" refId="ref6417" refString="CHIRON G. &amp; BELLONE R. 2005. - Les orchidees de Guyane francaise. Tropicalia, Voreppe; AFCEV, Villiers-les-Nancy, ii + 376 p." type="book" year="2005">Chiron &amp; Bellone (2005)</bibRefCitation>
, argued that 
<taxonomicName box="[443,579,917,943]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Isochilus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pauciflorus">
<emphasis box="[443,579,917,943]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="262">I. pauciflorus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was referable to a typical form of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Jacq.) R. Br." authorityName="R. Br." baseAuthorityName="Jacq." box="[310,571,949,975]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Isochilus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="linearis">
<emphasis box="[310,413,949,975]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="262">I. linearis</emphasis>
(Jacq.) R. Br.
</taxonomicName>
, but the diagnosis of the latter differs on several morphological points, among which is the auriculate-alate and briefly stipitate column in 
<taxonomicName box="[133,268,1044,1070]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Isochilus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="7" pageNumber="262" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pauciflorus">
<emphasis box="[133,268,1044,1070]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="262">I. pauciflorus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a detail clearly shown in its 
<typeStatus box="[580,681,1044,1070]" pageId="7" pageNumber="262">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
